snippet.title: Tarot Time with Andie
snippet.description: Tarot by Andie’s new channel for Pop culture, psychic insights,  crime and more,  keeping original channel strictly for Royal spreads on the British Monarchy.  Here I will diversify my tarot readings.  Add psychology when needed.  Welcome to my new adventure and yours 💫⭐️
